;
; Cornerstone
INUMBER 1778
NAME 295
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 2
SUBSTANCE STONE
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAM
This cornerstone will provide the foundation for a one room house on the specified street. The room may be decorated as you like with up to five pieces of furniture. The house comes complete with one mist-proof door, lockable on the outside with a key, and latchable on the inside, as well as a window which looks out on the street.

To submit your room description, assemble a document containing the description of the room, a list of furniture and accessories with a description of each, and a description of the actual house, yard and door. Send the document to BULLONEY in email.

At this time there is no way to include a container for permanent storage of items. Alarms, magic devices, additional rooms, secret doors, forges, cauldrons or other items which would give the player an advantage, are availble on staff approval per the published price list. House customization will be done on a first come, first serve basis, and depending on the demand, may take some weeks to complete.
*DESCRIPTION_END
