;
Variable chargeme
variable hahaha
Variable fight
variable irefuse
MACRO 11
IFVAR align < -2
	Equal fight 15
ENDIF
IFVAR align >= -2
	IFVAR ALIGN <= 3
		Equal fight 30
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR ALIGN > 3
	EQUAL FIGHT 60
ENDIF
ECHO OTHERS %N seems to struggle with %h weapon...
ECHO PLAYER You feel the weapon pressing its will against yours.
RANDOM IREFUSE 3 50 1
ADD IREFUSE FIGHT
IFVAR IREFUSE > WIL
	SUB IREFUSE WIL
	DAMAGE ELECTRIC IREFUSE The weapon fights its wielder!
	DAMAGE SLASH 6 The weapon tries to cut itself free.
ENDIF
;
; Sword
INUMBER 599
NAME 201
WEIGHT 10
VOLUME 5
SLASH_WEAPON
PARAMETER1 14
WIELDABLE
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAM
A strange symbol on the blade glimmers slightly.
*DESCRIPTION_END
SUBSTANCE HARDMETAL
IFVERB RECALL -1
	ECHO PLAYER This sword has the symbol of Dahkahn on the blade.
ENDIF
IFVERB WIELD -1
	CALL 11
ENDIF
IFVERB UNWIELD -1
	CALL 11
ENDIF
IFVERB CONCENTRATE -1
	RANDOM CHARGEME 3 75 1
	ADD CHARGEME FIGHT
	IFVAR WIL > CHARGEME
		ECHO OTHERS The weapon attempts to fight %n's will, but fails.
		SPELL 208 10
		SPELL 210 10
		SPELL 102 10
	ENDIF
	IFVAR WIL < CHARGEME
		RANDOM HAHAHA 2 25 1
		DAMAGE ELECTRIC HAHAHA The weapon refuses to submit!
		DAMAGE SLASH 6 The weapon tries to cut itself free.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
