			ECHO PLAYER You pull the pants back up to your waist.
			ECHO OTHERS %N pulls %a up from around %h ankles, where they were, to %h waist.
			EQUAL ITEMBIT0 0
			APPEAR %H pants cling snugly to %h fanny.
		ELSE
			ECHO PLAYER You tug your pants up a bit, adjusting them until you are comfortable.
			ECHO OTHERS %N tugs %h pants up a bit, adjusting them until comfortable.
