VARIABLE COINAGE
VARIABLE CHEAT
INUMBER 1223
NAME 229
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
MISC
IFVERB RUB -1
	ECHO PLAYER You feel luckier now!
	EQUAL CHEAT 1
ENDIF
IFPREVERB FLIP -1
	ECHO OTHERS %N flips the lucky coin into the air...
	ECHO PLAYER You flip the lucky coin into the air and hope for the best...
	RANDOM COINAGE 1 100 0
	IFVAR CHEAT = 1
		EQUAL COINAGE 35
	ENDIF
	IFVAR COINAGE > 0
		IFVAR COINAGE < 51
			ECHO ALL ...the coin lands heads up!
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
	IFVAR COINAGE > 50
		IFVAR COINAGE < 101
			ECHO ALL ...the coin lands tails up!
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
	EQUAL CHEAT 0
	CLEARVERB
ENDIF
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAM
You see a shiny copper penny with a portait of a man in profile on one side, and a picture of a building on the other.
*DESCRIPTION_END
VARIABLE LICKME
; Lipgloss
INUMBER 1224
NAME 1427
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
OPENABLE
IFPREVERB WEAR -1
	IFITEM -1 OPEN
		RANDOM LICKME 1 3 0
		IFVAR LICKME = 3
			ECHO OTHERS %N runs %h tongue over her lips and smiles at you warmly.
			ECHO PLAYER You carefully apply the lipgloss making sure it is not on your teeth.
		ENDIF
		IFVAR LICKME = 2
			ECHO OTHERS %N looks around for a place to see %h reflection so that %s can better apply the lips gloss.
			ECHO PLAYER You carefully apply the lipgloss.
		ENDIF
		IFVAR LICKME = 1
			ECHO OTHERS %N slowly and sensuosly applies gloss to %h puckered lips.
			ECHO PLAYER You pooch out your lips a bit and apply some gloss.
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
	IFITEM -1 CLOSED
		ECHO PLAYER You'll need to open it first.
	ENDIF
	CLEARVERB
ENDIF
