INUMBER 476
NAME 546
MISC
WEIGHT 2
VOLUME 5
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAMINE
The strange ball has deep black grooves in it that apportion the object
into numerous geometric shapes. Across the entire orange surface are
tiny bumps that don't seem to serve any obvious purpose. The ball is very
light as well, as if it were filled with nothing but air.
*DESCRIPTION_END
VARIABLE monbasketball
IFPREVERB RUB -1
  CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You begin bouncing the ball up and down off the floor with your hand, getting into a good rhythm...
    ECHO OTHERS %N begins bouncing the ball up and down off the floor with %h hands, getting into a good rhythm...
    PLREVENT 1
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER Choosing the right moment you quickly bend your knees, move one hand behind you and then push the ball between your open legs, dribbling it back and forth like that.
    ECHO OTHERS Choosing the right moment %N quickly bends %h knees, moves one hand behind %iself and then pushes the ball between %h open legs, dribbling it back and forth like that for some time.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR RNUM ! 234
   ECHO PLAYER You bounce the orange ball skillfully along the floor, letting your hand slap it back down when it bounces up against your palm.
   ECHO OTHERS %N bounces the orange ball skillfully along the floor, using %h hand to slap the ball back against the floor when it bounces up against %h hand.
  ENDIF
   IFVAR RNUM = 234
      RANDOM dummy2 1 100 0
      IFVAR dummy2 =< 15
       ECHO PLAYER You carefully set yourself, positioning the ball in your hands and concentrating on the metal hoop....
       ECHO OTHERS %N carefully sets %iself, positioning the ball in %h hands and concentrating on the metal hoop...
       PLREVENT 2
       CONTPLREVENT
       ECHO PLAYER You thrust your hands and arms towards the metal hoop, releasing the ball at the last moment and watching it carefully as it flies towards its target...
       ECHO OTHERS %N thrusts %h hands and arms towards the metal hoop, releasing the ball at the last moment and watching it carefully as it flies towards its target....
       PLREVENT 2
       CONTPLREVENT
       ECHO ALL The ball flies towards the metal hoop, ascending then descending in a somewhat graceful arc...
       PLREVENT 1
       CONTPLREVENT
       ECHO ALL The ball descends and.....
       PLREVENT 1
       CONTPLREVENT
       ECHO ALL .....TOTALLY MISSES the hoop....AIR BALL!!! %N looks a bit dejected as %s picks up the ball.
     ENDIF
      IFVAR dummy2 > 15
       IFVAR dummy2 =< 35
        ECHO PLAYER You carefully set yourself, positioning the ball in your hands and concentrating on the metal hoop....
        ECHO OTHERS %N carefully sets %iself, positioning the ball in %h hands and concentrating on the metal hoop...
        PLREVENT 2
        CONTPLREVENT
        ECHO PLAYER You thrust your hands and arms towards the metal hoop, releasing the ball at the last moment and watching it carefully as it flies towards its target...
        ECHO OTHERS %N thrusts %h hands and arms towards the metal hoop, releasing the ball at the last moment and watching it carefully as it flies towards its target....
        PLREVENT 2
        CONTPLREVENT
        ECHO ALL The ball flies towards the metal hoop, ascending then descending in a somewhat graceful arc...
        PLREVENT 1
        CONTPLREVENT
        ECHO ALL The ball descends and.....
        PLREVENT 1
        CONTPLREVENT
        ECHO ALL ...hits the rim and then ricochets right back into %N's hands! What a hosehead!
       ENDIF
      ENDIF
       IFVAR dummy2 > 35
        IFVAR dummy2 =< 55
          ECHO PLAYER You carefully set yourself, positioning the ball in your hands and concentrating on the metal hoop....
          ECHO OTHERS %N carefully sets %iself, positioning the ball in %h hands and concentrating on the metal hoop...
          PLREVENT 2
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO PLAYER You thrust your hands and arms towards the metal hoop, releasing the ball at the last moment and watching it carefully as it flies towards its target...
          ECHO OTHERS %N thrusts %h hands and arms towards the metal hoop, releasing the ball at the last moment and watching it carefully as it flies towards its target....
          PLREVENT 2
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO ALL The ball flies towards the metal hoop, ascending then descending in a somewhat graceful arc...
          PLREVENT 1
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO ALL The ball descends and.....
          PLREVENT 1
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO ALL ....hits the rim...and begins to roll around the rim...
          PLREVENT 1
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO ALL ...the ball slowly spins around the rim...then stops...hanging on the edge for a moment before...
          PLREVENT 1
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO ALL ...falling away from the hoop and back onto the floor where %N disconsolately retrieves it from. MISS!!!
        ENDIF
      ENDIF
        IFVAR dummy2 > 55
         IFVAR dummy2 =< 70
          ECHO PLAYER You carefully set yourself, positioning the ball in your hands and concentrating on the metal hoop....
          ECHO OTHERS %N carefully sets %iself, positioning the ball in %h hands and concentrating on the metal hoop...
          PLREVENT 2
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO PLAYER You thrust your hands and arms towards the metal hoop, releasing the ball at the last moment and watching it carefully as it flies towards its target...
          ECHO OTHERS %N thrusts %h hands and arms towards the metal hoop, releasing the ball at the last moment and watching it carefully as it flies towards its target....
          PLREVENT 2
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO ALL The ball flies towards the metal hoop, ascending then descending in a somewhat graceful arc...
          PLREVENT 1
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO ALL The ball descends and.....
          PLREVENT 1
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO ALL ....hits the rim...and begins to roll around the rim...
          PLREVENT 1
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO ALL ...the ball slowly spins around the rim...then stops...hanging on the edge for a moment before...
          PLREVENT 1
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO ALL  ...falling right through the hoop! A strange voice floats from the ball, "SCORE! ONE POINT FOR %N!"
         ENDIF
        ENDIF
         IFVAR dummy2 > 70
          IFVAR dummy2 =< 93
           ECHO PLAYER You carefully set yourself, positioning the ball in your hands and concentrating on the metal hoop....
           ECHO OTHERS %N carefully sets %iself, positioning the ball in %h hands and concentrating on the metal hoop...
           PLREVENT 2
           CONTPLREVENT
           ECHO PLAYER You thrust your hands and arms towards the metal hoop, releasing the ball at the last moment and watching it carefully as it flies towards its target...
           ECHO OTHERS %N thrusts %h hands and arms towards the metal hoop, releasing the ball at the last moment and watching it carefully as it flies towards its target....
           PLREVENT 2
           CONTPLREVENT
           ECHO ALL The ball flies towards the metal hoop, ascending then descending in a somewhat graceful arc...
           PLREVENT 1
           CONTPLREVENT
           ECHO ALL The ball descends and.....
           PLREVENT 1
           CONTPLREVENT
           ECHO ALL ....slams into the wooden sign and then drops neatly through the metal hoop! A strange voice floats from the ball, "SCORE! TWO POINTS FOR %N!"
          ENDIF
         ENDIF
          IFVAR dummy2 > 93
           ECHO PLAYER You carefully set yourself, positioning the ball in your hands and concentrating on the metal hoop....
           ECHO OTHERS %N carefully sets %iself, positioning the ball in %h hands and concentrating on the metal hoop...
           PLREVENT 2
           CONTPLREVENT
           ECHO PLAYER You thrust your hands and arms towards the metal hoop, releasing the ball at the last moment and watching it carefully as it flies towards its target...
           ECHO OTHERS %N thrusts %h hands and arms towards the metal hoop, releasing the ball at the last moment and watching it carefully as it flies towards its target....
           PLREVENT 2
           CONTPLREVENT
           ECHO ALL The ball flies towards the metal hoop, ascending then descending in a somewhat graceful arc...
           PLREVENT 1
           CONTPLREVENT
           ECHO ALL The ball descends and...
           PLREVENT 1
           CONTPLREVENT
           ECHO ALL ...flies straight as an arrow through the center of the hoop! A strange voice floats from the ball, "NOTHING BUT NET! SCORE! THREE POINTS FOR %N!"
          ENDIF
    ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PULL -1
  CLEARVERB
     IFVAR RNUM ! 234
         ECHO PLAYER You extend your arms to either side, palms down, and place the ball on the back of your right hand...
         ECHO OTHERS %N extends %h arms to either side, palms down, and places the orange ball on the back of %h right hand...
         PLREVENT 2
         CONTPLREVENT
         ECHO PLAYER You tilt slightly to the left and the ball begins to roll...you keep your balance perfectly as it rolls down your right arm...
         ECHO OTHERS %N tilts slightly to the left and the ball begins to roll...%N keeps %h balance perfectly as it rolls down %h right arm...
         PLREVENT 1
         CONTPLREVENT
         ECHO PLAYER ...the ball rolls up your right shoulder, slowing down slightly and then moving across your neck...almost falling off...but you manage to keep it moving...
         ECHO OTHERS ...the ball rolls up %N's right shoulder, slowing down slightly and then moving across %h neck...almost falling off...but %s manages to keep it moving....
         PLREVENT 1
         CONTPLREVENT
         ECHO PLAYER ...you straighten somewhat as the ball rolls over your left shoulder, down your arm and into your waiting hand...
         ECHO OTHERS ...%N straightens somewhat as the ball rolls over %h left shoulder, down %h left arm and into %h waiting hand...
         PLREVENT 1
         CONTPLREVENT
         ECHO PLAYER ...with a deft flick of your wrist you throw the ball up, beginning it spinning as you do and then catch it on your index finger where you let it spin for a while, finally letting it come to a stop and bowing.
         ECHO OTHERS ...with a deft flick of %h wrist %N throws the ball up into the air, it begins to spin as %s does so....%N then agilely catches the ball upon %h index finger and lets it spin for a whole before finally letting it come to a stop and bowing.
     ENDIF
    IFVAR RNUM = 234
           RANDOM DUMMY3 1 100 0
            IFVAR dummy3 =< 89
              ECHO PLAYER You step back from the hoop, finding yourself a long distance from the target now...
              ECHO OTHERS %N steps back from the hoop, going almost to the edge of the room before stopping...
              PLREVENT 2
              CONTPLREVENT
              ECHO PLAYER You take extra care to set yourself for the shot, spinning the ball once and then coming to a ready position...
              ECHO OTHERS %N takes extra care in setting %iself for the shot, spinning the ball once in %h hands then coming to a ready position...
              PLREVENT 2
              CONTPLREVENT
              ECHO PLAYER You leap up, releasing the ball with a mighty push at the top of your jump, and then watching it fly towards the target...
              ECHO OTHERS %N leaps up, releasing the ball with a mighty push at the top of %h jump, and then watching it fly towards the hoop....
              PLREVENT 1
              CONTPLREVENT
              ECHO ALL ...the ball flies towards the hoop, arcing gracefully, nearly touching the ceiling as it flies...
              PLREVENT 1
              CONTPLREVENT
              ECHO ALL ...the ball descends, almost in slow motion, heading for the hoop...
              PLREVENT 2
              CONTPLREVENT
              ECHO ALL ...CLANGGGG!!! The ball strikes the rim and shoots back into the hands of a dejected %N!
            ENDIF
             IFVAR dummy3 > 89
              ECHO PLAYER You step back from the hoop, finding yourself a long distance from the target now...
              ECHO OTHERS %N steps back from the hoop, going almost to the edge of the room before stopping...
              PLREVENT 2
              CONTPLREVENT
              ECHO PLAYER You take extra care to set yourself for the shot, spinning the ball once and then coming to a ready position...
              ECHO OTHERS %N takes extra care in setting %iself for the shot, spinning the ball once in %h hands then coming to a ready position...
              PLREVENT 2
              CONTPLREVENT
              ECHO PLAYER You leap up, releasing the ball with a mighty push at the top of your jump, and then watching it fly towards the target...
              ECHO OTHERS %N leaps up, releasing the ball with a mighty push at the top of %h jump, and then watching it fly towards the hoop....
              PLREVENT 1
              CONTPLREVENT
              ECHO ALL ...the ball flies towards the hoop, arcing gracefully, nearly touching the ceiling as it flies...
              PLREVENT 1
              CONTPLREVENT
              ECHO ALL ...the ball descends, almost in slow motion, heading for the hoop...
              PLREVENT 2
              CONTPLREVENT
              ECHO ALL ....SWIIIISSSSSHHH! Nothing but net as the ball flies perfectly through the hoop! A strange voice sounds from within the ball, "SCORE!!! FOUR POINTS FOR %N!"
             ENDIF
         ENDIF
ENDIF
