;
; (Crimson Band) Standard
INUMBER 1662
NAME 1103
SHIELD
ARTICLE THE
WEIGHT 7
VOLUME 20
*DESCRIPTION_START
Mounted on a tall, ivory-tipped rod carved from sturdy uquart, the Standard
of the Crimson Band flutters in the slightest breeze. Emblazoned on the
ancient, silk standard is a fierce eagle, wings spread, grasping a
brilliant star ruby in its talons.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB WIELD -1
 IFVAR ALIGN > -6
  IFVAR ALIGN < 6
   ECHO PLAYER A white glow forms around your hands, forming a thin film between your palms and the Standard as you wield it.
   ECHO OTHERS A white glow forms around %N's hands, forming a thin film between %h palms and the Standard as %s wields it.
  ENDIF
 ENDIF
 IFVAR ALIGN > 5
  ECHO PLAYER A white glow forms around your hands and then sinks into them as you wield the Standard.
  ECHO OTHERS A white glow forms around %N's hands and then sinks into them as %s wields the Standard.
 ENDIF
 IFVAR ALIGN < -5
  ECHO PLAYER A white glow forms around your hands, forcing them apart and preventing you from wielding the Standard.
  ECHO OTHERS A white glow forms around %N's hands, forcing them apart and preventing %i from wielding the Standard.
  CLEARVERB
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TURN -1
	IFITEM -1 WIELDED
	ECHO PLAYER As if every past wielder of the Standard loans you strength, you feel increased confidence and leadership ability. A voice in your mind cries, "sieze the moment!"
	ECHO OTHERS With great determination and fierceness, %N waves the Crimson Band Standard. The spectacle renews and revitalizes your respect for that organization.
	ROUTINE 1
	CLEARVERB
	ENDIF
ENDIF
