			IFVAR DUMMY2 = 4
				ECHO PLAYER You feel the touch of Myrna's mind:
				ECHO PLAYER "What's going on?  Somebody, please tell me!  What's going on?!?"
			ENDIF
			IFVAR DUMMY2 = 5
				ECHO PLAYER Your thoughts are jarred as you sense the death of Alge.
			ENDIF
			IFVAR DUMMY2 = 6
				ECHO PLAYER Your thoughts are jarred as you sense the death of Myrna.
			ENDIF
			IFVAR DUMMY2 = 7
				ECHO PLAYER Your thoughts are jarred as you sense the death of Oscare.
			ENDIF
			IFVAR DUMMY2 = 8
				ECHO PLAYER Your thoughts are jarred as you sense the death of Valusia.
			ENDIF
			IFVAR DUMMY2 = 9
