ENDIF
IFPREVERB LAUGH -1
IFVAR ITEMVAL5 = -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO PLAYER Nothing happens...which is expected since you got the amulet wet. Maybe you should have read the directions.
ELSE
	IFVAR ITEMVAL5 ! 1
		CLEARVERB
		ECHO PLAYER Your good feelings have a profound effect on the mood amulet, turning it to a nice shade of yellow.
		ECHO OTHERS %N's amulet slowly changes to a nice yellow color.
		EQUAL ITEMVAL5 1
		EQUAL ITEMADJ1 358
	ELSE
		CLEARVERB
		ECHO PLAYER The amulet is well aware of your feelings.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
