IFPREVERB CONCENTRATE -1
	IFVAR ITEMVAL5 = -1
		CLEARVERB
		ECHO PLAYER Nothing happens...which is expected since you got the amulet wet. Maybe you should have read the directions.
	ELSE
		IFVAR ITEMVAL5 ! 6
