					ECHO OTHERS %N drops %h mood amulet right in a big puddle. The crystal which composes the amulet turns black. %S snatches it back up, but the damage has been done.
					EQUAL ITEMVAL5 -1
					EQUAL ITEMADJ1 25
				ENDIF
			ENDIF
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
ENDIF
