;card
INUMBER 1797
NAME 681
MISC
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
SUBSTANCE PAPER
ARTICLE A
IFPREVERB PULL -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO PLAYER You put the card back into the deck.
	ECHO OTHERS %N puts a card back into the deck.
	REMOVEITEM -1
ENDIF
;
;chameleon sword
INUMBER 1798
NAME 201
SLASH_WEAPON
WEIGHT 8
VOLUME 6
SUBSTANCE HARDMETAL
ARTICLE A
PARAMETER1 9
IFPREVERB WIELD -1
	IFVAR ALIGN > 0
		ECHO PLAYER As you reach for your sword, it glows briefly with a white light.
		ECHO OTHERS %N's sword glows white as it is wielded.
		EQUAL ITEMVAL3 9
	ENDIF
	IFVAR ALIGN < 0
		ECHO PLAYER As you reach for your sword, it glows briefly with a red light.
		ECHO OTHERS %N's sword glows red as it is wielded.
		EQUAL ITEMVAL3 8
	ENDIF
	IFVAR ALIGN = 0
		EQUAL ITEMVAL3 0
	ENDIF
ENDIF
;
;crystal ball
INUMBER 1799
NAME 546
MISC
WEIGHT 15
VOLUME 4
SUBSTANCE BRITTLE
ARTICLE A
IFPREVERB GAZE -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO PLAYER You gaze into a crystal ball...%c
	ECHO OTHERS %N gazes into a crystal ball.
	MOD CHASBALLSTATE 6
	IFVAR ITEMVAL2 = 0
		IFVAR CHASBALLSTATE = 0
			ECHO PLAYER [Bazaar Center]%cYou revel in the tumult as the center of the Bazaar overwhelms your senses with%cits smell and sizzle of roast mutton, its cries of hawkers and cajoling%cmerchants. Street dancers, minstrels, and half-clad jugglers amuse the crowds%cnear a large marble fountain.
		ENDIF
		IFVAR CHASBALLSTATE = 1
			ECHO PLAYER [Bazaar Center]%cThis is the center of what used to be the Bazaar. It is now a smoking ruin.%cDead bodies lay everywhere, surrounded by rubble, and you can hear screams%coff in the distance. The smashed remains of a large fountain are here, amidst%cthe smoke and flames.
		ENDIF
		IFVAR CHASBALLSTATE = 2
			ECHO PLAYER [Town Center]%cYou see before you the center of a huge, thriving city. Tall buildings of%ca strange, alien architecture surround you, reaching to touch the sky. All%caround, people push past, dressed in strange, yet eerily familiar styles%cof clothing.
		ENDIF
		IFVAR CHASBALLSTATE = 3
			ECHO PLAYER [Village Square]%cThis small clearing marks the center of life for the simple folk%cwho live in this small village. It is where all meetings are held, and all%cbusiness is conducted. All around stand the plain thatch huts of the%cvillagers.
		ENDIF
		IFVAR CHASBALLSTATE = 4
			ECHO PLAYER [Cracked Wasteland]%cYou stand in the middle of a blasted and cracked wasteland, stretching%cto the horizon, as far as you can see, in every direction. There are no%csigns of life to be seen anywhere.
		ENDIF
		IFVAR CHASBALLSTATE = 5
			ECHO PLAYER [Thick Forest]%cTrees surround you; thick, full, tall trees, obscuring your vision.%cThe smell of rain mingles with the pungent smell of animals, and hangs%cin the air like a cloud. Chitters and chirps resound in the brisk air,%cand all kinds of small creatures scurry past. There is a small pond here,%cin the center of all the trees.
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
	IFVAR ITEMVAL2 = 1
		IFVAR CHASBALLSTATE = 0
			ECHO PLAYER You see the face of a mature woman whose features look strangely familiar.
		ENDIF
		IFVAR CHASBALLSTATE = 1
			ECHO PLAYER You see a dark aelfen wearing a black dress.
		ENDIF
		IFVAR CHASBALLSTATE = 2
			ECHO PLAYER You see a young, scholarly-looking man poring over an ancient text of some kind.
		ENDIF
		IFVAR CHASBALLSTATE = 3
			ECHO PLAYER You see a mature woman and a dark aelfen standing next to a magical portal of some kind.
		ENDIF
		IFVAR CHASBALLSTATE = 4
			ECHO PLAYER You see a vast, starry void, with many wispy, tentacled shapes floating within.
		ENDIF
		IFVAR CHASBALLSTATE = 5
			ECHO PLAYER You see a young scholar, studying an old book, with the faint image of an old man in a straitjacket superimposed over it.
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
	RANDOM DUMMY1 1 5 0
	ADD CHASBALLSTATE DUMMY1
	MOD CHASBALLSTATE 6
ENDIF
;
;black ring of chaos
INUMBER 1348
NAME 167
MISC
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
SUBSTANCE SOFTMETAL
ARTICLE THE
WORN_RING
IFPREVERB TWIST -1
        IFVAR ITEMVAL5 ! TIM
        	CLEARVERB
	        ECHO PLAYER You twist your ring, feeling strange forces at work.
                ECHO OTHERS %N twists a ring...
                ECHO ALL A gnomen appears!
                GENMON 136
                EQUAL ITEMVAL5 TIM
        ENDIF
ENDIF
